---
title: Smart Double Chicken Patty Salad with DIY Ranch Dressing
description: All the flavours of wing night in a starch-free supper that features tender chicken patties, an easy-to-cook swap for wings at home. Crisp celery is like the delicious dippers you enjoy with spicy wings.

